# Yoga Virtual Coach — Implementation Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A full real-time yoga pose coaching backend using **FastAPI + MoveNet Thunder TFLite**.

---

## Bugs Fixed

| File | Bug | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| [movenet.py](file:///d:/Python_Projects/yoga-backend/app/services/movenet.py) | Wrong import path for `dataset_builder` | Changed to `app.services.dataset_builder` |
| [movenet.py](file:///d:/Python_Projects/yoga-backend/app/services/movenet.py) | Stale `joint` var in body keypoints loop | Changed to [BodyPart(idx)](file:///d:/Python_Projects/yoga-backend/app/services/dataset_builder.py#24-43) |
| [preprocess.py](file:///d:/Python_Projects/yoga-backend/scripts/preprocess.py) | Wrong import paths | Fixed to full package paths |
| [preprocess.py](file:///d:/Python_Projects/yoga-backend/scripts/preprocess.py) | [detect()](file:///d:/Python_Projects/yoga-backend/app/services/preprocess.py#24-39) NameError — `detection` never initialised | Added proper initialisation + fallback |
| [preprocess.py](file:///d:/Python_Projects/yoga-backend/scripts/preprocess.py) | Deprecated `np.str` | Replaced with [str](file:///d:/Python_Projects/yoga-backend/app/routers/pose.py#83-111) |
| [preprocess.py](file:///d:/Python_Projects/yoga-backend/scripts/preprocess.py) | Top-level script code ran on every import | Wrapped in class/functions |
| [trainer.py](file:///d:/Python_Projects/yoga-backend/app/services/trainer.py) | Class names inconsistent between train/test CSV | Derived from sorted unique values |

---

## New Files Created

```
scripts/
  preprocess.py       ← CLI: extract keypoints from images → CSV
  train.py            ← CLI: train classifier → .keras + class_names.json

app/
  data/
    pose_references.json   ← ideal joint angles per pose class
  schemas/
    pose.py                ← Pydantic: KeypointSchema, PoseFrameResponse
  services/
    pose_service.py        ← MoveNet singleton (loads once at startup)
    classifier_service.py  ← Keras classifier (lazy-loaded)
    angle_service.py       ← Joint angle calc + coaching feedback
  routers/
    pose.py                ← POST /pose/classify  +  ws /pose/stream
```

